description.narrative:
The Fund will have a high development impact, which includes but is not limited to:
(i) Reduction of GHGs; 
(ii) Adoption of more environmentally sustainable practices;
(iii) Improvement in clean energy technology in China;
(iv) Job creation including in the frontier regions; 
(v) Demonstration effect by strengthening investee companies and making them targets for acquisition and investments;
(vi) Privatization of renewable energy assets developed by SOEs; and
(vii) Developing and financing renewable energy projects in the frontier regions of China.
